@startuml REQ-VAL-005 Return tag enforcement
autonumber
skinparam maxMessageSize 200
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

box "System" #LightBlue
  participant "Validate" as Validate
  participant "Config" as Config
end box

header
  **REQ-VAL-005: Return tag enforcement**
  //Description:// Non-void functions with doxygen must have @return or\n@returns tag
  //Acceptance Criteria:// Non-void functions without @return produce violations; void\nfunctions and exemption-tagged functions are exempt;\nrequire_return config controls enforcement
end header


Validate -> Config: get_validate(config)
loop func in functions
end loop

@enduml